Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.61,0:03:47.20,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}感情的烈馬 一旦任之脫韁
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.58,0:03:50.37,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}便再也找不到方向
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.08,0:03:58.75,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}罪惡的扳機 本已沾染血光
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.09,0:04:02.05,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}卻漸漸辨不清形狀
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.01,0:04:07.85,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}若要將恨意驅趕出心房
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.68,0:04:13.44,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}還如何讓你把命償?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.02,0:04:19.32,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}掘塵封過往
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.40,0:04:25.45,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}只為填罪業汪洋
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.70,0:04:30.66,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}怨凜冽鋒芒
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.87,0:04:37.34,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}頷首撫刻骨心傷
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.00,0:04:45.47,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}苦痛亦盡數遺忘
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.64,0:04:49.01,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}身陷曲折迴廊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.56,0:04:56.94,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}既迷失原本模樣
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.15,0:05:00.48,OPCN-CHT,,0,0,0,,{\fade(200,200)\be5}何不遁世韜光?
